<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Model Application | International Productions</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #0a0a0a; color: #e5e5e5; font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif; }
        .gold-text { color: #d4af37; }
        .input-field { background: #1a1a1a; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 12px; border-radius: 4px; width: 100%; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-6 md:p-20">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <header class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest gold-text">Casting Call</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Seeking Female Models (Age 18-25) for International Erotic Productions</p>
        </header>

        <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Opportunity</h2>
                <p class="mb-4 text-gray-400">Join a professional set as a muse and model. We focus on high-end visuals, branding, and career development.</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                    <li>✓ Professional Video & Photography</li>
                    <li>✓ International Distribution</li>
                    <li>✓ Portfolio Building (Get your own copy)</li>
                    <li>✓ Intimate & Professional Atmosphere</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-lg">
                <form action="YOUR_MAIL_SERVICE_OR_BACKEND" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-xs uppercase mb-1">Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" class="input-field" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-xs uppercase mb-1">Age (Must be 18-30)</label>
                        <input type="number" name="age" min="18" max="30" class="input-field" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-xs uppercase mb-1">Location / Instagram</label>
                        <input type="text" name="socials" class="input-field" placeholder="@handle or City">
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <label class="block text-xs uppercase mb-1">Upload Photos (Clear Face & Body)</label>
                        <input type="file" name="photos" class="text-sm" multiple required>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-yellow-600 hover:bg-yellow-700 text-black font-bold py-3 uppercase tracking-tighter transition">Apply Now</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
